## Session start protocol

At every session start:

1. Read this file (AGENT.md)
2. Read `PROJECT.md` — goals, anti-goals, success criteria
3. Read `ARCHITECTURE.md` — stack, structure, quality gates
4. List `phases/` — identify the FIRST phase where `verify/phase-NN.sh` does not exist or fails
5. Read that phase file
6. Begin execution

Do NOT read ahead. Only the current phase file is in scope.

